{"tid":1430612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港激光節！！","createTime":"2019-08-07T19:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T19:32:59.000Z","uid":80024,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7ecae26d475311994c423e3c29189847893452f0","tid":1430612,"uid":80024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:19:27.000Z","msg":"今日真係好撚開心<br />\n廿幾歲人拎住技筆high到咁自己都覺得好膠<br />\n不過呢種尋日頹到喊今日笑到喊嘅感覺<br />\n香城ocamp咁！<br />\n真係得夢中嘅兄弟姊妹先明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所 以 好 希 望 每 年 都 有 激 光 節！</span><br />\n比香港人搵返單純嘅快樂<br />\n87又好 七夕又好<br />\n比香港一個跳舞唱歌玩水玩燈嘅夜晚<br />\n<br />\n重點係<br />\n禁止商業化咗件事<br />\n香港消費文化已經太重個個節日都鼓吹消費<br />\n唔準賣嘢呀 例如搞到變market乜乜77<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後唔洗擔心<br />\n我冇娛樂化件事<br />\n黎緊我會帶住今日嘅開心繼續行落去<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 #缺一不可"},{"pid":"9f5e31fe3b0f966c2dc392748aa54b72c0a0a20a","tid":1430612,"uid":80024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:23:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"889d77ae18ea95920209e86e505fdcb3c3f29e1a","tid":1430612,"uid":80024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:23:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6f5b5f4b4299975e067bc599ef207c4cebaff88c","tid":1430612,"uid":80024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:23:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2fbc399fba74eed783ba6b387a0e8a2f0916b705","tid":1430612,"uid":80024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:32:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}